### ============================================================
### BASIC
### ============================================================

### All Books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books

### All Authors
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Authors

### ============================================================
### FILTER - COMPARISON OPERATORS
### ============================================================

### String comparison
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=genre eq 'Fantasy'

###
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=status ne 'Cancelled'

###
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=country eq 'India'

### Number comparison
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=price gt 10

###
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=stock lt 50

###
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=rating ge 4.0

### Boolean comparison
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=isActive eq true

###
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=isAvailable eq false

### Date comparison
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=publishDate gt 2020-01-01

###
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=orderDate le 2026-06-01

### UUID comparison
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=ID eq 3f4a2b1c-d5e6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890

### Null checks
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=email eq null

###
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=phone ne null

### ============================================================
### FILTER - LOGICAL OPERATORS
### ============================================================

### Range query
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=price ge 10 and price le 20

### OR
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=genre eq 'Fantasy' or genre eq 'Mystery'

### AND
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=isActive eq true and stock lt 10

### Multiple conditions
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=orderDate ge 2026-01-01 and status ne 'Cancelled'

###
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=rating ge 4.5 and price lt 15

### Parentheses
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=(genre eq 'Fantasy' or genre eq 'Mystery') and price lt 15

### ============================================================
### FILTER - STRING FUNCTIONS
### ============================================================

### Contains
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=contains(title,'Harry')

### Contains Lord
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=contains(title,'Lord')

### Starts with H
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=startswith(title,'H')

### Ends with .com
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=endswith(email,'.com')

### Case insensitive search
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=contains(tolower(title),'harry')

### ISBN starts with 978
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=startswith(isbn,'978')

### ============================================================
### FILTER - DATE FUNCTIONS
### ============================================================

### Orders placed in 2026
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=year(orderDate) eq 2026

### Employees hired in June
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=month(hireDate) eq 6

### Books published after 2000
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=year(publishDate) gt 2000

### Orders from June 2026
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=year(orderDate) eq 2026 and month(orderDate) eq 6

### ============================================================
### FILTER - ARITHMETIC OPERATORS
### ============================================================

### Stock below minimum
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=stock sub minStock lt 0

### Total amount greater than 50
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=quantity mul unitPrice gt 50

### Discount greater than 3
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=price sub discountedPrice gt 3

### ============================================================
### $SELECT
### ============================================================

### Only title
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$select=title

### Title and price
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$select=title,price

### Title, price and rating
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$select=title,price,rating

### Title and author FK
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$select=title,author

### ============================================================
### $EXPAND
### ============================================================

### Expand full author
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$expand=author

### Expand author name
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$select=title&$expand=author($select=name)

### Expand author name and country
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$expand=author($select=name,country)

### Authors with books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Authors?$expand=books

### Authors with book titles only
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Authors?$expand=books($select=title)

### Authors with top 2 expensive books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Authors?$expand=books($orderby=price desc;$top=2)

### ============================================================
### ASSOCIATION FILTERING
### ============================================================

### Books by Rowling
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=author/name eq 'J.K. Rowling'

### Books by Tolkien
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=author/name eq 'J.R.R. Tolkien'

### Books by USA authors
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=author/country eq 'USA'

### ============================================================
### $ORDERBY
### ============================================================

### Cheapest books first
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=price

### Most expensive books first
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=price desc

### Highest rated books first
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=rating desc

### Alphabetical by title
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=title

### Genre then title
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=genre,title

### Newest orders then highest price
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=orderDate desc,price desc

### Genre A-Z then price high-low
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=genre asc,price desc

### ============================================================
### $TOP
### ============================================================

### First 3 books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$top=3

### First 5 books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$top=5

### Top 3 most expensive books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=price desc&$top=3

### Top 3 highest rated books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=rating desc&$top=3

### ============================================================
### $SKIP
### ============================================================

### Skip first 2 books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$skip=2

### Skip first 5 books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$skip=5

### ============================================================
### PAGINATION ($TOP + $SKIP)
### ============================================================

### Page 1
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=title&$top=3&$skip=0

### Page 2
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=title&$top=3&$skip=3

### Page 3
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=title&$top=3&$skip=6

### Cheapest 4 books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=price&$top=4

### Next 4 cheapest books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=price&$top=4&$skip=4

### ============================================================
### $COUNT
### ============================================================

### Count all books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books/$count

### Count with results
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$count=true

### Count fantasy books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books/$count?$filter=genre eq 'Fantasy'

### Count with pagination
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=title&$top=3&$skip=3&$count=true

### ============================================================
### $SEARCH
### ============================================================

### Search Harry
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$search=Harry

### Search Design
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$search=Design

### ============================================================
### COMBINED REAL-WORLD QUERIES
### ============================================================

### Top 3 cheapest fantasy books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=genre eq 'Fantasy'&$orderby=price&$top=3&$select=title,price

### Genre then price desc with count
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=genre,price desc&$top=2&$skip=0&$count=true

### Books containing 'the', rating >= 4
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=contains(tolower(title),'the') and rating ge 4.0&$orderby=rating desc&$select=title,rating

### Active fantasy books under $20
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=isActive eq true and genre eq 'Fantasy' and price lt 20&$orderby=price

### Top 5 books with author details
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$top=5&$expand=author($select=name,country)

### Most expensive tech books
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=genre eq 'Tech'&$orderby=price desc&$select=title,price,rating